<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-002-199 </DOCNO><DOCID>11 594 846</DOCID><JOURNAL>PC Week  Dec 9 1991 v8 n49 p34(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Ziff-Davis Publishing Co. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Business Forecast program gains scripting files, new file formats.andO;(Business Forecast Systems Inc. introduces Forecast Pro Batch1.1)(brief article) (Product Announcement)andM;</TITLE><DESCRIPT>Company:   Business Forecast Systems Inc. (Product introduction).andO;Product:   Forecast ProBatch 1.1 (Data analysis software) (Productintroduction).andO;Topic:     Product IntroductionFinancial softwareData Analysis.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>For business users and scientists who forecast large sets of data, BusinessForecast Systems Inc. is offering a version of its batch-process forecastingprogram that adds new file formats, reports and statistics-handlingcapabilities.andM;Forecast Pro Batch version 1.1, like earlier releases, lets users forecastmultiple sets of data -- for multiple product lines, for example -- whenlooking at each series is not practical, according to officials at BusinessForecast Systems.andM;Users of Forecast Pro Batch write script files that contain data to beforecast, and the software executes the commands automatically.andM;New reports in version 1.1 of the forecasting program include an item report,containing a one-line description for each product forecast, and a summaryreport, a more detailed forecast evaluation.andP;  New file formats include threeWK1 (Lotus 1-2-3) formats -- a row format, a line format and a named rangeformat -- allowing users to forecast data in large spreadsheets.andM;New statistical functions include the ability to set upper and lowerconfidence (error factor) limits separately, and the ability to specify thehandling of missing data values.andM;Forecast Pro Batch is priced at $3,995; Forecast Pro Batch 500, whichforecasts a maximum of 500 items, is priced at $1,995.andP;  Both are availablenow.andM;Business Forecast Systems is a privately held company that specializes inforecasting software.andM;The Belmont, Mass., company can be reached at (617) 484-5050.andO;</TEXT></DOC>